<div class="update-item">
    <div class="update-item__title">New Transport Layer Support Added</div>
    <div class="update-item__description">
        The rust-libp2p implementation now supports WebTransport connections, enabling better browser compatibility. This was implemented in <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://github.com/libp2p/rust-libp2p/pull/1234">PR #1234</a> and follows the spec discussion in <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://github.com/libp2p/specs/issues/567">specs#567</a>.
    </div>
</div>

<div class="update-item">
    <div class="update-item__title">Fix: Remove Redundant EventLoopGroup Handling</div>
    <div class="update-item__description">
        A fix was made to remove redundant EventLoopGroup handling in the swift-libp2p implementation. This change was merged in <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://github.com/swift-libp2p/swift-libp2p/pull/44">PR #44</a>.
    </div>
</div>

<div class="update-item">
    <div class="update-item__title">Fix: Add TLS Support for Python Tests</div>
    <div class="update-item__description">
        A fix was made to add TLS support for python tests in the libp2p/test-plans repository. This change was merged in <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://github.com/libp2p/test-plans/pull/798">PR #798</a>.
    </div>
</div>

<div class="update-item">
    <div class="update-item__title">New Echo Protocol Interoperability Tests Added</div>
    <div class="update-item__description">
        New echo protocol interoperability tests were added to the libp2p/test-plans repository. This change was merged in <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://github.com/libp2p/test-plans/pull/800">PR #800</a>.
    </div>
